
Important Sepecification
-The App should be run on an Android phone running at least 2.3
-Device must have SD
-Photos Can only be taken in Portrait 


Compiling and Running Code from Scratch

1) Place entirety of "TheCagifier" folder into Eclipse project

2) Run as... Android Application

3) Press Continue button or wait 10 seconds to proceed to Main screen

4) Press Switch Camera Button to Switch Between Front and Back Camera

4) Press Take Photo Button to Capture photo or Upload button to select photo from Gallery

6) Press Download Button to Save Picture to Gallery

7) Press Back Button to return to Main Screen
